1699", "productType": "clips", "musicInfo": {"artist_name": "Project Pat", "song_name": "Life We Live (feat. Namond Lumpkin, Edgar Fletcher)", "uses_original_audio": false, "should_mute_audio": false, "should_mute_audio_reason": "", "audio_id": "3185212188396377"}, "isCommentsDisabled": false}, {"id": "3291671594010173413", "type": "Video", "shortCode": "C2uXd_uOF_l", "caption": "Growing your cleaning team is just a dream unless...\n\nYou take time to invest in your own leadership development....\n\nI know when I came into this industry I didn't know how to hire, fire, or retain employees so I dealt with the struggles a lot of cleaning businesses go through when hiring...\n\nDelegating is crucial for growing a strong clean team... \n\nAnd I get it, this is your baby, but if you create the policies, procedures, foundations, train, coach and follow up with your team, things will flow smoothly...\n\nBasically it all comes down to developing your leadership skills so you can continue to become the best leader for your team...\n\nThen watch your team take you to the next level!!\n\nComment \"TEAMS\" if you need help growing a team in 2024\n\n#cleaningcommunity\n#cleaningbusiness\n#CleaningBusinessSuccess\n#Cleanpreneurship", "hashtags": ["cleaningcommunity", "cleaningbusiness", "CleaningBusinessSuccess", "Cleanpreneurship"], "mentions": [], "url": "https://www.instagram.com/p/C2uXd_uOF_l/", "commentsCount": 0, "dimensionsHeight": 852, "dimensionsWidth": 480, "displayUrl": "https://instagram.flas1-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t51.71878-15/498594505_1418503535844295_3180182327435316966_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&_nc_ht=instagram.flas1-2.fna.fbcdn.net&_nc_cat=107&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gGwFhZyi0KKTMsl2HpfVGbvlPlmi5ngb3f3lPqRPIbilvd57weVsOTH1YaeXiJEb1c&_nc_ohc=y7uUPj4C9tQQ7kNvwHtX0gE&_nc_gid=YWVoe6jPpgD7W9ohjO9o-w&edm=AOQ1c0wBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_AQDZopz4TKfTTdT55bQC1cOB2k4VUIZA237aTkMUDjM8wg&oe=6A61A85A&_nc_sid=8b3546", "images": [], "videoUrl": "https://instagram.flas1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/o1/v/t2/f2/m