This way we are not setting ourselves up for failure and disappointment.\n\n2. If you have staff, allow your staff to help create the expectations...This allows your team to feel like they're a part of the decision making process and they will feel more obligated to meet expectations that they helped create themselves.\n\n3. Clearly communicate expectations and provide defined strategies... It's key to never assume that your staff understands your expectations. You need to communicate them clearly and ask to have them repeated to you so you know that expectations are understood. And it's our job to provide strategies as well so our team can execute and meet our expectations.\n\nComment \"EXPECTATIONS\" if you're looking to grow a team in 2024 or need help with your team!\n\n#cleaningcommunity\n#cleaningbusiness\n#Cleanpreneurship \n#CleaningBusinessSuccess\n#cleanersofinstagram", "hashtags": ["cleaningcommunity", "cleaningbusiness", "Cleanpreneurship", "CleaningBusinessSuccess", "cleanersofinstagram"], "mentions": [], "url": "https://www.instagram.com/p/C2r5yX1OUJp/", "commentsCount": 1, "dimensionsHeight": 1350, "dimensionsWidth": 1080, "displayUrl": "https://instagram.flas1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t51.82787-15/654031135_18061158911433742_7511191057141007573_n.webp?stp=dst-jpg_e15_fr_p1080x1080_tt6&_nc_ht=instagram.flas1-1.fna.fbcdn.net&_nc_cat=110&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gGwFhZyi0KKTMsl2HpfVGbvlPlmi5ngb3f3lPqRPIbilvd57weVsOTH1YaeXiJEb1c&_nc_ohc=KrQkMsQzaGsQ7kNvwEVQar2&_nc_gid=YWVoe6jPpgD7W9ohjO9o-w&edm=AOQ1c0wBAAAA&ccb=7-5&ig_cache_key=MzI5MDk3ODA5NjQyMDM0NTg4Ng%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&oh=00_AQBnyrfrro8yYo-O6cktfywFfE1btnTZGiVQ8-y-ILYWTA&oe=6A61C251&_nc_sid=8b3546", "images": ["https://instagram.flas1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t51.82787-15/654031135_18061158911433742_7511191057141007573_n.webp?stp=dst-jpg_e15_fr_p1080x1080_tt6&_nc_ht=instagram.flas1-1.fna.fbcdn.net&_nc_cat=110&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gGwFhZyi0KKTMsl2HpfVGbvlPlmi5ngb3f3lPqRPIbilvd57weVsOTH1YaeXiJEb1c&_nc_ohc=KrQkMsQzaGsQ7kNvwEVQar2&_nc_gid=YWVo